Bloodthorn is a tough, wiry plant found in Carceri, the Outlands, the Abyss, and Pandemonium. It has dry, black vines, small-bladed leaves, and lush reddish berries. 
It feeds on the blood of its victims. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Planescape Monstrous Compendium Appendix II